First, we need to calculate the prefix matrix of the given matrix. Then we can make changes to each element in it according to given 'k'.
For prefix matrix, pre[i][j] = pre[i-1][j] + pre[i][j-1] - pre[i-1][j-1]

**Time and Space Complexities :** Time Complexity : O(mxn), Auxiliary Space : O(mxn)

