 example of step to get dp[2][2] (the last one on the bot-right)
*  we want this part![image](https://assets.leetcode.com/users/images/754c1718-e7a7-4cbb-b7f7-2e0b86a16873_1631033419.5090227.png)
*  so we get `prefix[2][2]` which is equal to 45 so the sum of all matrix ![image](https://assets.leetcode.com/users/images/5e49b9a9-b6e9-479a-be9a-c02d9599635e_1631033363.605127.png)
* from that we remove the top part ![image](https://assets.leetcode.com/users/images/be1ec77a-981f-4ac6-8a8d-ea0aed446aca_1631033449.1404293.png)
* then we remove the left part ![image](https://assets.leetcode.com/users/images/7bc15293-eb4d-42ea-8544-ab6ab4d9a62f_1631033472.9346817.png)
* since we remove the top left part twice we need to add it back ![image](https://assets.leetcode.com/users/images/10e4a526-a078-4de9-8055-fba6a30ca427_1631033525.752147.png)
* now we get the part that we want. 


