**Explanation**
1. First, we will create a 2D vector named dp where `dp[i][j]` is the sum of all cells from `(0,0)` to `(i,j)`.
2. Then we will build our ans vector, where `ans[i][j] = dp[i+k][j+k] - dp[i-k-1][j+k] - dp[i+k][j-k-1] + dp[i-k-1][j-k-1];`
3. Finally return the vector `ans`.
