    At first we have to find size of Node in order to find the specific value from Nth element from end using loop.
    Then substract k from size of Node which means we can find it using loop which starts from beginning.
    And again Run loop from beginning another 2 new pointers points
those 2 elements from start and end.
    After loop just change the values and return the node.


# Approach
